{"name":"Block Agent ","dsl":{"schema":"2.0","config":{"update_multi":true,"style":{"text_size":{"normal_v2":{"default":"normal","pc":"normal","mobile":"heading"}}}},"body":{"direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"12px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","elements":[{"tag":"img","img_key":"IMG_KEY_TODO","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","corner_radius":"8px","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**:GoGoGo:  一句话生成 AI 仪表盘组件，让数据可视化更加出彩**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","flex_mode":"stretch","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"8px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"<font color='blue'>**核心亮点** \n</font>","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"- **类型丰富**：一句话生成高级图表，桑基、热力、玫瑰、瀑布、水波等图表任你探索","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"- **全局兼容**：仪表盘生态全兼容，支持下钻看明细、筛选联动，体验比肩原生组件","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"- **编辑自由**：对话式精调组件颜色、图例、坐标轴等属性，细节一调即成","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-50","padding":"12px 8px 12px 8px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"8px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"<font color='blue'>**适用场景** \n</font>","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"- **流量归因**：用桑基图看用户流向、玫瑰图对比来源占比，归因路径一目了然","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"- **运营监控**：用热力图看活跃分布、水波图看目标进度，关键指标一眼掌握","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"- **财务拆解**：用瀑布图看收入增减、矩形树图呈现成本分布，资金去向清晰可见\n","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-50","padding":"12px 8px 12px 8px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"我们还帮你准备了快速上手的秘籍，快来试试吧 👇","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"hr","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","flex_mode":"stretch","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"button","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"快速上手秘籍"},"type":"primary","width":"fill","size":"medium","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"buzz_outlined"},"behaviors":[{"type":"open_url","default_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/832596162602-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84-ai-%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6","pc_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/832596162602-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84-ai-%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6","ios_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/832596162602-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84-ai-%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6","android_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/832596162602-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84-ai-%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6"}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","weight":1},{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","element